game_description: This is NOT the main version of VRChat! Do not use this version unless you are testing beta features for VRChat. This is a separate version of VRChat used for beta testing. In most cases, you will NOT be able to join non-beta users when using this version of VRChat. You may encounter unexpected behavior and bugs as a result. When beta tests are not running, this application will be identical to the live version of VRChat. To learn more about what's going on with the VRChat BETA, please join our Discord server! https://discord.gg/vrchat You can install the main version of VRChat at the following link: https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/1856672347794301/
